definition: to take money or valuables out of storage/to recover/to ship goods/to extract (chemicals from solution)

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc
variant of 出[chu1] (classifier for plays or chapters of classical novels)

sentences.english: We do not entertain buyer who do not pay in full!
sentences.chinese: 如果买主没付全款，本人有权不出货。

sentences.english: Each order contains 2 packs of 96 tablets at one flat shipping rate.
sentences.chinese: 每个订单包含96片2包在一个单位出货率。

sentences.english: Sample arrangement for the bank transfer and fast safe shipping.
sentences.chinese: 安排样办，进行银行转汇并快速安排安全出货。

sentences.english: Your order can go out on Monday.
sentences.chinese: 你们的订货在星期一就可以出货。

sentences.english: Scrutinizing shipping window summary and coordinating with USO for any mistake occurred.
sentences.chinese: 仔细审核出货订单汇总如有任何错误和美国联系解决。

sentences.english: Please ship the remaining products as soon as possible, because the factory has no more space now.
sentences.chinese: 请尽快安排剩余产品出货，现在工厂已经放不下了。

sentences.english: Non-compliant product in production or unshipped will be rejected.
sentences.chinese: 生产中的和尚未出货的违规产品将被拒收。

sentences.english: Benefiting from MTK's transformation, Spreadtrum's shipment has boosted up.
sentences.chinese: 展讯则受益联发科转型，出货量大增。

sentences.english: What reference is made to the delivery note number?
sentences.chinese: 出货单的单号是否有参考文件？

sentences.english: What are the suppliers Pre-delivery Inspection &Controls?
sentences.chinese: 供应商如何进行出货前的检验和控制？

sentences.english: Nope … the volume is too high for that. BTW, why would they?
sentences.chinese: 老大不会觉得是机构拉高准备出货？

sentences.english: Inside the mine, the domestic market is stable, the situation is general.
sentences.chinese: 内矿方面，国产矿市场平稳，出货情况一般。

sentences.english: The import factor will handle your collection after sales.
sentences.chinese: 进口保理商将在出货后处理你的应收款。

sentences.english: Do you carry out pre-shipment inspections independent from the factory?
sentences.chinese: 是否请工厂以外的第三方进行出货前验货？

sentences.english: Bring up repacking time before appoint shipping goods.
sentences.chinese: 未指定出货前提出翻箱时间。
